  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_61E17DF0-22CF-0135-4992-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In Course Navigation, click the <strong>Settings</strong> link.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_course_details" data-step-uuid="f1f29f39-20c7-411b-beec-69993a9fcbfc">
