    <p>Click the Course Details tab.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="organize_epub_by_content_type" data-step-uuid="067e3179-036d-4790-a2c4-c17a01e7d382">
    <h2 id="organize_epub_by_content_type" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Organize ePub by Content Type</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/000/791/729/original/945df281-1270-4214-b0b5-8a908aaaa59b.png" srcset="" alt="Organize ePub by Content Type" height="47" width="493">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_61E1E500-22CF-0135-4996-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In the Course Details tab, locate the ePub Export section. Click the <strong>Organize ePub by content type </strong>checkbox.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="update_course_details" data-step-uuid="d7fd136b-ee92-4599-83a6-8e4752cacb9e">
